    Format[edit]

    • Regular Season:
      • Round-Robin format league
        • All teams play each other once
        • All matches are Bo3
      • Top 6 teams advance to the Playoffs
        • Top 2 teams advance to Upper Bracket Round 2
        • Next 4 teams advance to Upper Bracket Round 1
    • Playoffs:
      • Double-Elimination bracket
      • All matches (excl. Grand Final) are Bo3
      • Grand Final is Bo5
